         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e650"> </a>Loosen the screws (4), to remove the U-bolt (D) of support (A) and release handlebar (6).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e652"> </a>Duly support the handlebar.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e654"> </a>Loosen the screws (5) from U-bolt (E) and remove support (A) from lower U-bolts (F).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_4_004602764.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e659"> </a>Reposition handlebar (6) on lower U-bolts (F) and fasten it with the upper U-bolt (E).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e661"> </a>Apply recommended grease on screws (5) and tighten them to a torque of 25 Nm ± 5%.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_4_004702765.jpg"></center>
